name: Utazumi Sakurako - Blue Archive (Character)
description:
This is a LORA of the charcter Utazumi Sakurako from Nexon Games' Blue Archive. New in this replacement version is higher detail, flexibility in prompting, her normal nun dress, fixed resolution, and can now be prompted without clothes tags.

To prompt her nun dress enter "<lora:Sakurako-BlueArchive-v2:strength>Sakurako, nun dress, nun hood, thighhighs, halo," To prompt her latex outfit enter "<lora:Sakurako-BlueArchive-v2:strength>Sakurako, black latex outfit, black latex nun hood, black latex thighhighs, halo,"

I like this LORA the best at around 0.7 strength. Trained on Anythingv4.5 with Clip Skip 2.

This is a remake of version 2, which had overfitting issues. This is a far superior model.
